{
    "zh-CN": {
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_NAME": "HUNK",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_DESCRIPTION": "HUNK是一名精英渗透者，携带通过OSP（现场采购）获得的大量武器。<color=#CCD3E0>\n\n< ! > 對较弱敌人使用战斗刀以节省弹药。\n\n< ! > 获取G-病毒样本将为您提供一张钥匙卡，允许在每个阶段访问武器箱。\n\n< ! > 在敌人或攻击性投射物附近使用Quickstep进行完美闪避，然后用主武器反击。\n\n< ! > 弹药稀缺，但可以在打开的箱子中找到。副武器库存和冷却缩减也会影响弹药。\n\n< ! > 这是战争。生存是您的责任。 <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SUBTITLE": "收割者",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_OUTRO_FLAVOR": "..然后他离开了，一切安好。",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_OUTRO_FAILURE": "..然后他消失了，人类单位现已中和。",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_DEFAULT_SKIN_NAME": "默认",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_CLASSIC_SKIN_NAME": "RE2make",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_TOFU_SKIN_NAME": "豆腐",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SUPER_SKIN_NAME": "<color=#FFFF00>Early Supporter</color>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_LIGHTWEIGHT_SKIN_NAME": "轻量",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_GUERRILLA_SKIN_NAME": "士兵",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_ROOKIE_SKIN_NAME": "新兵",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SWAT_SKIN_NAME": "维和者",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_LEON_SKIN_NAME": "Specialist",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_LEONSHIRT_SKIN_NAME": "Specialist EX",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_ENFORCER_SKIN_NAME": "Bulldozer",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_WESKER_SKIN_NAME": "Mastermind",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_DOOM_SKIN_NAME": "Slayer",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_COMMANDO_SKIN_NAME": "Commando",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_JACKET_SKIN_NAME": "夹克",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_PPASSIVE_NAME": "OSP（现场采购）",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_PPASSIVE_DESCRIPTION": "HUNK可以收集<color=#FFFF00>U.C.钥匙卡</color>来打开<style=cIsDamage>武器箱</style>并扩展他的 arsenal。 <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_PPASSIVE2_NAME": "被遗忘的士兵",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_PPASSIVE2_DESCRIPTION": "每个阶段第一个死亡的<style=cIsHealth>首领</style>会掉落一个包含武器或配件的<style=cIsDamage>补给包</style>。 <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_PASSIVE_NAME": "暗影战斗",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_PASSIVE_DESCRIPTION": "以一把<style=cIsDamage>LE 5</style>和一件<style=cIsDamage>副武器</style>开始。你可以<style=cIsDamage>搜寻</style><style=cIsUtility>箱子</style>寻找弹药。 <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_PASSIVE2_NAME": "迫近的恐惧",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_PASSIVE2_DESCRIPTION": "以一个<style=cIsDamage>完整的军火库</style>开始，<style=cIsHealth>但是</style>你无法再<style=cIsHealth>获得额外弹药</style>。 <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_RANDOMPASSIVE_NAME": "New Game+",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_RANDOMPASSIVE_DESCRIPTION": "以一把<style=cIsDamage>LE 5</style>和一件<style=cIsDamage>副武器</style>开始。你可以<style=cIsDamage>搜寻</style><style=cIsUtility>箱子</style>寻找弹药。<style=cIsHealth>所有武器箱内容都是随机的。</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOTGUNPASSIVE_NAME": "最高权威",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOTGUNPASSIVE_DESCRIPTION": "以一把<style=cIsDamage>W-870</style>和一件<style=cIsDamage>副武器</style>开始。你可以<style=cIsDamage>搜寻</style><style=cIsUtility>箱子</style>寻找弹药。 <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SMGPASSIVE_NAME": "至高佣兵",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SMGPASSIVE_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsHealth>仅</style>以一把<style=cIsDamage>完全升级的LE 5</style>开始。你可以<style=cIsDamage>搜寻</style><style=cIsUtility>箱子</style>寻找弹药。<style=cIsDamage>特殊</style>被替换为<color=#C80202>混乱模式</color>。 <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_WPASSIVE_NAME": "全面全球饱和",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_WPASSIVE_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsHealth>仅</style>以一件<style=cIsDamage>副武器</style>开始。你可以<style=cIsDamage>搜寻</style><style=cIsUtility>箱子</style>寻找弹药。<style=cIsDamage>实用</style>被替换为<color=#C80202>Uroboros</color>。 <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_FLAMERPASSIVE_NAME": "纵火狂",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_FLAMERPASSIVE_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsHealth>仅</style>以一个<style=cIsDamage>化学火焰喷射器</style>开始。你可以<style=cIsDamage>搜寻</style><style=cIsUtility>箱子</style>寻找弹药。<style=cIsHealth>每个阶段仅出现一个武器箱。</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_PRIMARY_KNIFE_NAME": "战斗刀",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_PRIMARY_KNIFE_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>拔出。</style><style=cIsDamage>切割</style>附近的战斗人员造成<style=cIsDamage>200%伤害</style>，施加<style=cIsHealth>残废</style>。 <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_PRIMARY_CQC_NAME": "CQC（近距离战斗）",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_PRIMARY_CQC_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>拔出。</style><style=cIsDamage>踢两次</style>造成<style=cIsDamage>200%和250%伤害</style>。如果<style=cIsUtility>第二踢</style>命中，接上<style=cIsDamage>反击</style>。 <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_PRIMARY_RELOAD_NAME": "装弹",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_RELOAD_DESCRIPTION": "装填当前武器。 <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SECONDARY_AIM_NAME": "稳定瞄准",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SECONDARY_AIM_DESCRIPTION": "瞄准，<style=cIsUtility>暴露敌人弱点</style>。<style=cIsDamage>瞄准时使用主武器会开火当前装备的武器。</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_UTILITY_DODGE_NAME": "Quickstep",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_UTILITY_DODGE_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>前进</style>一小段距离。如果预防性地用于<style=cIsUtility>躲避攻击</style>，则执行<style=cIsDamage>完美闪避</style>。 <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_UTILITY_DODGE_SCEPTER_NAME": "Uroboros",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_UTILITY_DODGE_SCEPTER_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>前进</style>一小段距离。如果预防性地用于<style=cIsUtility>躲避攻击</style>，则执行<style=cIsDamage>完美闪避</style>。Uroboros的力量在你体内流淌。 <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_UTILITY_PARRY_NAME": "格挡",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_UTILITY_PARRY_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>格挡</style>一次攻击，<style=cIsDamage>抵消</style>伤害并<style=cIsUtility>返还冷却时间</style>。如果预防性地使用，执行<style=cIsDamage>完美格挡</style>。 <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_UTILITY_BASH_NAME": "肩撞",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_UTILITY_BASH_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>撞击</style>附近敌人，<style=cIsUtility>眩晕他们</style>造成<style=cIsDamage>400%伤害</style>。如果预防性地用于<style=cIsUtility>取消攻击</style>，执行<style=cIsDamage>完美偏转</style>。 <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SPECIAL_SWAP_NAME": "军团",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SPECIAL_SWAP_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>切换</style>到<style=cIsDamage>不同的武器</style>。轻触切换到<style=cIsUtility>上次使用的武器</style>。 <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SPECIAL_MAYHEM_NAME": "混乱模式",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SPECIAL_MAYHEM_DESCRIPTION": "进入<style=cIsDamage>混乱模式</style>，大幅提升武器性能。 <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_CONFIRM_NAME": "确认",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_CONFIRM_DESCRIPTION": "继续当前能力。 <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_CANCEL_NAME": "取消",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_CANCEL_DESCRIPTION": "取消当前能力。 <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_DEFAULT_NAME": "战斗刀",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_DEFAULT_DESCRIPTION": "一把标准军用刀。在关键时刻肯定有用。 <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_INFINITE_NAME": "战斗刀 EX",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_INFINITE_DESCRIPTION": "一把经过特殊处理、硬化到不可思议程度的军用刀。据说它是为了真正持久而制造的。 <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_HIDDEN_NAME": "隐藏刀片",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_HIDDEN_DESCRIPTION": "藏在袖子里的低调可伸缩刀片。非常适合潜行行动。 <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_WESKER_NAME": "定制刀",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_WESKER_DESCRIPTION": "一把带有锯齿边缘的残酷刀片，用于撕裂对手。 <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_MACHETE_NAME": "砍刀",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_MACHETE_DESCRIPTION": "一把主要用于游击战术的巨大刀片。 <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_RE4_NAME": "主刀",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_RE4_DESCRIPTION": "一把充满无限可能锻造的刀。 <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_BLOODY_NAME": "血染刀片",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_BLOODY_DESCRIPTION": "一把带血的锯齿刀片，已经撕裂了许多对手。 <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_HOTDOGGER_NAME": "HOT DOGGER",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_HOTDOGGER_DESCRIPTION": "顾名思义，这把由Umbrella开发的 anti-bioweapon 刀被那些喜欢炫耀的人使用。 <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_STUNROD_NAME": "电击棒",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_STUNROD_DESCRIPTION": "警告：实际上不会眩晕。 <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_KITCHEN_NAME": "菜刀",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_KITCHEN_DESCRIPTION": "一把用于烹饪的刀。刀片容易碎裂。 <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_SMG_NAME": "开火",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_SMG_DESCRIPTION": "射击造成<style=cIsDamage>110%伤害</style>。<style=cIsUtility>25%爆头加成。</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_M19_NAME": "开火",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_M19_DESCRIPTION": "射击造成<style=cIsDamage>500%伤害</style>。<style=cIsUtility>100%爆头加成。</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_SG09_NAME": "开火",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_SG09_DESCRIPTION": "射击造成<style=cIsDamage>500%伤害</style>。<style=cIsUtility>50%爆头加成。</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_BROOMHC_NAME": "开火",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_BROOMHC_DESCRIPTION": "射击造成<style=cIsDamage>180%伤害</style>。<style=cIsUtility>25%爆头加成。</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_MAGNUM_NAME": "开火",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_MAGNUM_DESCRIPTION": "射击造成<style=cIsDamage>1,200%伤害</style>。<style=cIsUtility>50%爆头加成。</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_GOLDGUN_NAME": "开火",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_GOLDGUN_DESCRIPTION": "射击造成<style=cIsDamage>99,999%伤害</style>。<style=cIsUtility>50%爆头加成。</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_MUP_NAME": "开火",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_MUP_DESCRIPTION": "射击造成<style=cIsDamage>320%伤害</style>。<style=cIsUtility>25%爆头加成。</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_REVOLVER_NAME": "开火",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_REVOLVER_DESCRIPTION": "射击造成<style=cIsDamage>1,200%伤害</style>。<style=cIsUtility>50%爆头加成。</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_COLT_NAME": "开火",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_COLT_DESCRIPTION": "射击造成<style=cIsDamage>2,000%伤害</style>。<style=cIsUtility>50%爆头加成。</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_SPARKSHOT_NAME": "开火",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_SPARKSHOT_DESCRIPTION": "发射带电针造成<style=cIsDamage>1,000%伤害</style>。<style=cIsUtility>弹跳至多3名敌人造成<style=cIsDamage>2,000%伤害</style>。</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_BLUEROSE_NAME": "开火",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_BLUEROSE_DESCRIPTION": "射击造成<style=cIsDamage>2x3,800%伤害</style>。<style=cIsUtility>50%爆头加成。</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_SHOTGUN_NAME": "开火",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_SHOTGUN_DESCRIPTION": "射击造成<style=cIsDamage>14x150%伤害</style>。<style=cIsUtility>50%爆头加成。</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_M3_NAME": "开火",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_M3_DESCRIPTION": "射击造成<style=cIsDamage>10x130%伤害</style>。<style=cIsUtility>50%爆头加成。</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_SSG_NAME": "开火",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_SSG_DESCRIPTION": "射击造成<style=cIsDamage>16x200%伤害</style>。<style=cIsUtility>50%爆头加成。</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_STREETSWEEPER_NAME": "开火",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_STREETSWEEPER_DESCRIPTION": "射击造成<style=cIsDamage>14x24%伤害</style>。<style=cIsUtility>25%爆头加成。</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_SLUGGER_NAME": "开火",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_SLUGGER_DESCRIPTION": "射击造成<style=cIsDamage>3,000%伤害</style>。<style=cIsUtility>50%爆头加成。</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_AR_NAME": "开火",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_AR_DESCRIPTION": "射击造成<style=cIsDamage>385%伤害</style>。<style=cIsUtility>50%爆头加成。</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_MINIGUN_NAME": "开火",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_MINIGUN_DESCRIPTION": "射击造成<style=cIsDamage>2x250%伤害</style>。<style=cIsUtility>伤害随攻击速度提升。</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_ATM_NAME": "开火",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_ATM_DESCRIPTION": "射击造成<style=cIsDamage>8,000%伤害</style>。<style=cIsUtility>直接命中造成更多伤害。</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_ATM2_NAME": "开火",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_ATM2_DESCRIPTION": "射击造成<style=cIsDamage>8,000%伤害</style>。<style=cIsUtility>直接命中造成更多伤害。</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_RPG_NAME": "开火",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_RPG_DESCRIPTION": "射击造成<style=cIsDamage>8,000%伤害</style>。<style=cIsUtility>直接命中造成更多伤害。</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_ROCKETLAUNCHER_NAME": "开火",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_ROCKETLAUNCHER_DESCRIPTION": "射击造成<style=cIsDamage>12,000%伤害</style>。<style=cIsDamage>燃烧弹。</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_GRENADELAUNCHER_NAME": "开火",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_GRENADELAUNCHER_DESCRIPTION": "射击造成<style=cIsDamage>3,200%伤害</style>。<style=cIsDamage>燃烧弹。</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_MGL_NAME": "开火",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_MGL_DESCRIPTION": "射击造成<style=cIsDamage>2,400%伤害</style>。 <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_RAILGUN_NAME": "开火",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_RAILGUN_DESCRIPTION": "射击造成<style=cIsDamage>20,000%伤害</style>。 <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_FLAMETHROWER_NAME": "开火",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_FLAMETHROWER_DESCRIPTION": "喷射火焰造成<style=cIsDamage>巨量伤害</style>。<style=cIsUtility>点燃。</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_SCANNER_NAME": "扫描",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_SCANNER_DESCRIPTION": "扫描寻找<style=cIsUtility>未打开的武器箱</style>。 <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_HOOKSHOT_NAME": "钩爪",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_HOOKSHOT_DESCRIPTION": "向<style=cIsUtility>远处地点</style>发射钩子，然后<style=cIsUtility>将自己拉过去</style>。<style=cIsDamage>落地后可以反击。</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_KEYWORD_MANGLED": "残废",
        "ROB_HUNK_KEYWORD_COUNTER": "反击",
        "ROB_HUNK_KEYWORD_PERFECTDODGE": "完美闪避",
