        "ROB_HUNK_ITEM_EFFECT_BANDOLIER": "弹药包用<color=#00FF66>虚假弹药</color>装填你的弹匣。",
        "ROB_HUNK_ITEM_EFFECT_ALIENHEAD": "收集任何弹药时获得<style=cIsUtility>更多弹药</style>。",
